headline: Should You Reassess Teradyne After Its 18% Weekly Surge and AI Market Rally?
summary: Thinking about whether to buy, sell, or hold Teradyne? You are definitely not alone right now. Investors have been watching the automation and robotics space closely, and Teradyne has delivered some remarkable share price growth over both short and long timeframes. Over the past week, the stock surged 18.5%, capped off by a 17.2% climb over the last month and a solid 77.4% gain over three years. That kind of momentum tends to turn heads, though it can also mean increased volatility as risk...

headline: Stock Index Futures Muted Ahead of U.S. PMI Data and Powell’s Speech
summary: December S&P 500 E-Mini futures (ESZ25) are down -0.04%, and December Nasdaq 100 E-Mini futures (NQZ25) are down -0.06% this morning as investors remain on the sidelines ahead of a speech from Federal Reserve Chair Jerome Powell and U.S. business activity data.
